<title>USA: SubMicron to sell unit to BOC Group.</title>
<headline>SubMicron to sell unit to BOC Group.</headline>
<dateline>ALLENTOWN, Pa. 1997-06-30</dateline>
<text>
<p>SubMicron Systems Corp said Monday it had entered into an agreement for BOC Group Inc to buy assets and assume liabilities related to Systems Chemistry Inc, a subsidiary of SubMicron.</p>
<p>Details of the agreement were not disclosed, but SubMicron said the deal would generate about $20 million at closing that it will use to reduce its bank debt.</p>
<p>SubMicron said it expects the transaction to close during the third quarter.</p>
<p>BOC Group Inc is part of BOC Group Plc.</p>
